tweet: For most nations, farmer well-being should be viewed as of utmost importance. For that reason we must put politics aside & analyze India’s new farm bills & their economic implications. I shall soon make my analysis available & would love to hear the arguments of those who differ.

tweet: One more good reason to settle with the farmers. And avoid more hasty, ill-considered decisions taken without consultation that hurt people AND cost the nation's exchequer, like demonetisation, no-notice lockdown & the farm bills.
